snippet.title: Tiny House Giant Journey
snippet.description:
Hi, I'm Jenna. I built and lived in a Tiny House to free up my finances so that I can travel the world! On this YouTube channel, I share Alternative dwellings, lifestyle videos, unique and tiny vacation rentals, and my travel adventures around the planet. My story has been featured on HGTV, Travel Channel, the Huffington Post, USA Today, and many more! 

New video every Friday :) 

For more information, or to request be featured, go to my website: www.tinyhousegiantjourney.com
